title: Bobby Comes Clean + Josh Turner Talks About Meeting Johnny Cash + Show Member Unfollowed Bobby On Instagram

description:
Bobby brings his girlfriend Caitlin in to come clean about something he said on the show yesterday. Josh Turner talks about the time he went to Johnny Cash’s house and knocked on the door because he wanted to meet him. Plus, Bobby finds out someone on the show unfollowed him on Instagram!
